{"tid":1002913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華演唱會公布退票安排","createTime":"2019-01-31T09:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T09:26:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03c9315a658fe2475362b9b3e48cfc573eb3894b","tid":1002913,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"藝人劉德華早前因病取消七場演唱會，主辦機構公布退票安排。<br />\n<br />\n主辦機構在社交網站公布，早前接獲康文署書面通知，十二月香港體育館場地租用申請不獲接納，故未能安排補場演出。<br />\n<br />\n退票將分為兩個階段，第一階段，持門票人士填寫退票表格，連同門票正本以郵寄方式辦理退票，主辦機構會補貼35元郵費；而第二階段，於五月下旬持門票人士可以到香港體育館現場辦理退票手續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E9%80%80%E7%A5%A8%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92-072106261.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2594%25B1%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%2580%2580%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%258E%2592-072106261.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=37748550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E9%80%80%E7%A5%A8%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92-072106261.html</a>"}]}